title: Chilling new details in armed kidnap of Wisconsin girl Jayme close, brutal murder of her mom & dad
itunes:title: Chilling new details in armed kidnap of Wisconsin girl Jayme close, brutal murder of her mom & dad
description:
Jayme Closs is still missing a week after her parents were found shot dead in their Wisconsin home, but new details are emerging about what police know in the two murders and apparent kidnapping of the 13-year-old. Nancy Grace explores the latest in the case with forensics expert  Joseph Scott Morgan, Atlanta juvenile judge & lawyer Ashley Willcott, North Carolina divorce & family lawyer Kathleen Murphy, and syndicated radio host Dave Mack.
